{"tid":1274884,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"路西法效應","createTime":"2019-07-01T17:30:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-09T06:06:47.000Z","uid":175748,"like":36,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"5ea8d890dc94512de438b00541fa0ec5cf9203dd","tid":1274884,"uid":175748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T17:30:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/2X5W8mM_Wek\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F2X5W8mM_Wek&d=qB%2BEr1lTQcBPVU2CyFsNokuhYyo0AmqkWOXXUYRqYBI%3D&h=b3ef0b67\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/2X5W8mM_Wek</a><br />\n<br />\n平時睇happy kongner都淨係睇籃球<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n原來其他片都好撚高質<br />\n大家如果嫌長唔想睇可以自己search路西法效應<br />\n或條片頭10分鐘係講路西法效應<br />\n<br />\n我一路都唔明點解狗係咁無人性<br />\n終於有得解，我地最最最要推翻係極權政府<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a69fddd46afa8e69ec5594fc91cf46d6d019406","tid":1274884,"uid":204352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T17:32:07.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"4a67e183a07edfddb894773f80ae9ad65c62e112","tid":1274884,"uid":176017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T17:32:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"163e7638472ad06fbbb6ee1d937dd3f0001ac4e5","tid":1274884,"uid":175748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T17:57:22.000Z","msg":"如果睇完真係覺得好中既<br />\n幫手share下都得架"},{"pid":"85d83ee215fa56fdabc1487e6b7859d936d57aed","tid":1274884,"uid":175748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T02:48:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0bb46ffbd6a3344c6032075b98f9cd8dff185d41","tid":1274884,"uid":46681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T02:53:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5639f81c219f6344d9f5b5221015dba63bcc4654","tid":1274884,"uid":60057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T03:01:11.000Z","msg":"其實睇完除左幫黑警洗白外仲有咩用?"},{"pid":"57b90530f8209a032bddaaef5d8a85c3c9dc466a","